Here is an exmaple how to use a static method, just for frank_ and others who dont understand:

[code=java]public class StaticTest {
	public static void main(String[] args){		
		System.out.println(new StaticTest().staticMethod("frank_"));
	}

	public static String staticMethod(String name){
		String s = "Hello " + name + " !";
		return s;
	}	
}
[/code]

output
Hello frank_ !
